# cc-cockpit hosts — one line per source:
#
#   <label>|local|claude agents --json     this machine (reads sessions directly)
#   <label>|ssh|<user@host>                 remote machine (via the dedicated key)
#
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
# Easiest way to add a remote host:  ./scripts/add-host.sh <label> <user@host>
# After manual edits, reload the service (see README → "Manage").

local|local|claude agents --json

# Examples (replace with your own):
# build01|ssh|deploy@build01.internal
# gpu|ssh|ubuntu@10.0.0.5
